{
  "stem": "7455.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they invited me simply so that I should clean up the kitchen and do the dishes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I came back to the-- to the camp, stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the bombs being this near Cologne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Day and night, they were bombing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES] we heard rumors that they already on the Rhine, on the river Rhine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And day and night, there were bombs and we ran to the chimney.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then one time-- at one time, we knew that because of the factory and so, they're going to bomb.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're going to die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I and another girl, we wal-- went back at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We walked back to Witzhelden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a girl there, a guard and a girl that she was kind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't go to the Richters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went because she had somebody else already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we stayed there at the outskirts of the town for safety.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then the war was over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The English and Americans occupied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was-- when they took me away and when the factory was sort of fell apart because they didn't have coal, so we were at loose ends.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the one in charge left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So you are on your own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's when I went to the Witzhelden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as the war lingered on, I had a job at-- at some-- at a woman, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was a dentist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I stayed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the girl Maria that went with me also found a job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in-- in her house, we were hiding in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she would say, God knows what our Fuehrer's doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He meant well for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It just didn't turn out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
